Ethics management at Siemens In our business activities, we are committed to going beyond

laws and regulations. Our BCGs define how we interpret our responsibility, what is expected of all employees, and how we act as a company.

Our ethical principles have been integrated in the updated version of our BCGs. Responsible business conduct with all stakeholders and consistent consideration of Ethical Principles are expected in our decisions and are becoming increasingly important in view of the many changes and challenges in the world. Accordingly, we firmly anchored them in our BCGs: